[android](https://github.com/alibaba/weex/tree/android)分支的代码已修复该问题，测试效果如下：    
![QQ20161129-0@2x.png](https://ooo.0o0.ooo/2016/11/29/583d4ed918b1a.png)    
Test case：    
```vue
<template>
    <div>
        <div style="width: 200px;height: 200px;background-color: antiquewhite;margin: 60px">
            <div class="div-flag">
                <text class="text-flag">测试是</text>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</template>
<style>
    .div-flag {
        transform: rotate(45deg);
        -ms-transform: rotate(45deg); /* IE 9 */
        -moz-transform: rotate(45deg); /* Firefox */
        -webkit-transform: rotate(45deg); /* Safari 和 Chrome */
        -o-transform: rotate(45deg); /* Opera */
        position: absolute;
        top: -37px;
        right: -37px;
        width: 140px;
        height: 30px;
        background-color: red;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        /*overflow-clip: ;*/
        margin-top: 53px;
        margin-bottom: 53px;
    }
</style>
```

